<%= @greeting %>, <%= @user.full_name %>

  Thank you for you recent order from buy-local-art.com. While we are committed to providing you great
  local art, we are currently in development phase.
  Your card has not been charged for any recent purchases,
  but the artists have been notified of your interest in their work. We've included the artists' contact
  information below should you want to reach out. Thank you for your support! We looks forward
  to getting this great app into production soon!!

  Your order confirmation number is #<%= @order.order_confirmation %>.

  Order details:
  <% @order.order_items.each do |order_item| %>
      Piece: <%= order_item.piece.title %>
      Artist: <%= order_item.piece.artist.shop_name %>
      Quantity: <%= order_item.quantity %>
      Price: <%= number_to_currency order_item.total_price %>
  <% end %>

  Artist(s):
  <% @artists.each do |artist| %>
      Artist: <%= artist.shop_name %>
      Location: <%= artist.city_state %> (<%= artist.location %>)
      Email: <%= artist.user.email %>
      Phone: <%= number_to_phone artist.user.phone %>
  <% end %>

